Author: reitzensteinm
Content: "Rose said that context was also an issue for Digg; stories are being buried under the weight of noise making it more and more difficult for users to seek out and find niche stories. Digg is developing a smart suggestion system that will consider the type of stories a user has dugg previously then suggest similar stories based on that history."
